name: Printers Are From HELL
description:
How mutch can you print?

You need to print something important but as always your printer is not cooperating its your job to solve the printer problems and print as much as you can before the timer runs out!

Its free and Its just as fun as real printing!

Printer battle music by pant0don: http://opengameart.org/content/glitchy-battle

Engine and power down sound by qubodup: http://opengameart.org/users/qubodup

Thanks for looking at my games page.
If you experience any bugs leave a comment bellow and i will try my best to fix it!

Feedback is also appreciated just leave a comment below!

(this game requires Love2d)
